data.description: This home is located in one of the best neighborhoods in town Bedford/Carlisle line! Hardwood floors throughout, large interior room sizes, front to back Livingroom with fireplace.Upper level has 4 good size bedrooms with large closets and hardwood flooring, the master bedroom having a walk in closet as well.  Open concept living on the 1st floor, light and bright with sliders and french doors that lead onto two rear back decks.  A good size fenced in private wooded lot that also has a babbling brook for those tranquil  summer nights. . A little TLC will go a long way in this jem!.
